OL,6,FAn investigation into the
OL,7,Fcircumstances around the incidents is
OL,8,Funderway and enquiries ongoing.
OL,10,FAt this time no arrests have been made.
OL,12,FSupt Craig Kelshaw, of place-based
OL,13,Fsuperintendent for Lancaster and
OL,14,FMorecambe, said: "We are urging
OL,15,Fparents to be vigilant after a number
OL,16,Fof young people were taken ill after
OL,17,Fsmoking vapes believed to contain
OL,18,Fillegal drugs.
