OL,3,CVape warning after five teenagers fall
OL,4,Cill in Lancashire
OL,6,F"In recent weeks, police have become
OL,7,Faware of several incidents across
OL,8,FLancaster and Morecambe, with students
OL,9,Fat some schools and colleges taken ill
OL,10,Fand requiring hospital treatment.
OL,12,F"The legal age to use and purchase
OL,13,Fvapes is 18, however, we know that
OL,14,Fthey are being sold to young people
OL,15,Fvia social media, and these are then
OL,16,Fbeing taken into schools and colleges.
OL,18,F"Not only is this a health issue, but
OL,19,Fthose possessing and supplying illegal
OL,20,Fdrugs could be committing criminal
OL,21,Foffences.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
