OL,3,CVape warning after five teenagers fall
OL,4,Cill in Lancashire
OL,6,F"We are working closely with local
OL,7,Fschools and partners to share
OL,8,Finformation and intelligence.
OL,10,F"We would also urge parents, guardians
OL,11,Fand anyone with information they may
OL,12,Fhave about those supplying these vapes
OL,13,Fto call Lancashire Police on 101."
OL,15,FCllr Michael Green, Lancashire County
OL,16,FCouncil's cabinet member for Health
OL,17,Fand Wellbeing, added: "We are very
OL,18,Fconcerned about the latest spate of
OL,19,Fyoung people becoming ill after using
OL,20,Fvapes believed to have contained
OL,21,Fillegal drugs across Lancashire.
