OL,6,F"We know that our young people are
OL,7,Fobtaining these substances often via
OL,8,Fsocial media and using them in school
OL,9,Fsettings.
OL,11,F"Vaping illegal and unknown substances
OL,12,Fcarries significant health risks
OL,13,Fincluding becoming immediately unwell,
OL,14,Floss of consciousness and even risk to
OL,15,Flife and we urge everyone to do their
OL,16,Futmost to be vigilant and aware of the
OL,17,Fvery significant dangers.
