OL,6,F"If you are concerned about a young
OL,7,Fperson using drugs and vapes, please
OL,8,Fcontact specialist support charity We
OL,9,Fare With You   Twitter, Instagram,
OL,10,FFacebook   Linktree' via their website
OL,11,For on 0808 164 0074.
OL,13,F"We have also responded to the
OL,14,FGovernment consultation in support of
OL,15,Fstronger national action to address
OL,16,Fthe unscrupulous marketing of vapes
OL,17,Fthat are targeted at our young people."
